        "text": "A decapod dinghy can carry up to 30 Bulk of creatures or unattended items on their back, such as five Medium creatures. The anemones' gentle hold on the passengers is sufficient in most situations, but while in combat, those passengers are slowed 1 if they want to take other actions while remaining on the decapod dinghy's back.",
