            "text": "The decapod dinghy's anemones sting any number of creatures they choose among passengers and those the decapod dinghy has grabbed or restrained. The stings deal 5d6 poison damage (DC 26 basic Fortitude save). On a failed save, that creature is also enfeebled 2 for 1 hour.",
